    title: "Client Projects and Deliverables",
    content: `
      <p>For client projects, the ownership of deliverables and intellectual property rights will be governed by the specific agreement between Coalbanks Creative and the client. Unless otherwise specified in a written agreement:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
