      <p>We provide information to help copyright holders manage their intellectual property online. If you think somebody is violating your copyrights and want to notify us, please contact us at copyright@coalbanks.com.</p>
    `
  },
  {
    title: "Modifying and Terminating our Services",
    content: `
      <p>We are constantly changing and improving our Services. We may add or remove functionalities or features, and we may suspend or stop a Service altogether.</p>
      <p>You can stop using our Services at any time, although we'll be sorry to see you go. Coalbanks Creative may also stop providing Services to you, or add or create new limits to our Services at any time.</p>
